Summary 

This role is to involve in sourcing, screen and interview candidate by preparing candidate for the job while the whole process will be managed by Principal Consultant or Manager they report to. 

Key responsibilities: 

-	Independently search for candidates with familiarity of all sourcing channels based on job description; 
-	Timely input good candidates’ CV into Profile system; 
-	Communication with candidates via telephone and conduct face-to-face interview to select qualified candidates and gain useful information; 
-	Identify qualified candidates and submit results with solid reasons; 
-	Prepare candidate during interview session to make it success; 
-	Present sufficient candidate information when attending Morning Review; 
-	Achieving daily, monthly and quarterly KPIs consistently; 

Key requirements: 

-	Bachelor’s degree with 1-2 years’ experience with previous recruitment experience as a plus; 
-	Good communication and interpersonal skill; 
-	Ability to thrive in a fast-pace and performance-drive environment; 
-	Demonstrate high level of self-driven and self-motivated spirit;

岗位职责:
1、负责发布招聘信息、收集筛选简历并安排面试，利用各种有效招聘途径满足部门的招聘需求;
2、维护、拓展招聘渠道，开展有效招聘，并根据各岗位实际情况建立相应的人才库;
3、总结招聘工作存在的问题，提出优化招聘制度、流程的合理化建议，完成招聘分析报告;
4、协助贯彻公司制度政策及流程在所支持部门的执行;
5、其它人力资源支持工作。
任职要求:
1、本科及以上学历，人力资源及行政管理相关专业优先;
2、有制造业社招工作经验优先;
3、熟知人力资源管理、心理学等各类相关知识;熟悉相关法律、法规;
4、沟通协调能力突出，抗压能力强。
